{"tid":1894092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個有愛嘅故事！","createTime":"2020-02-23T16:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T20:02:54.000Z","uid":347895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2516f3e0fc07a4217cdfa7b546139c30e00546","tid":1894092,"uid":347895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"我知道宜家香港，甚至好多地方國家都好黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n我想收集大家身邊嘅好人好事，大家身邊嘅愛，無論係前線手足嘅互相扶持，定係親情、愛情、友情或者事業上嘅大事，甚至乎今日遇到一小件微不足道嘅小事，只要有愛有正能量，歡迎你放享。<br />\n<br />\n我哋想凝聚呢股正能量，將愛同正義嘅種子會係每個人心入面慢慢葫芽，感染開去。"},{"pid":"bb45c336b3a84821040744d67696796e3288f66b","tid":1894092,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"想聽前線的愛情故事"},{"pid":"0d1f1bbc620492f4647635284cb9bad3a91302e2","tid":1894092,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd33a0d4f7b5b0b4eea7893a3d0c5f05a6c89a1","tid":1894092,"uid":347895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb45c336b3a84821040744d67696796e3288f66b","tid":1894092,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"想聽前線的愛情故事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"我都想<br />\n推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b748ab71e2504bf09086ea8363b572b4841795","tid":1894092,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T20:02:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}